rows.label: tlk43310148_02_msg0001
rows.name:
Which flamin' mongrel bust open
the Holy Gate of Fontana?

rows.label: tlk43310148_02_msg0002
rows.name:
They built these massive gates
so they'd even stand up to
full-frontal assaults from Blades.

rows.label: tlk43310148_02_msg0003
rows.name:
It had to be pretty tough. It's to
stop the Cloud Sea flooding in when
the Divine Beast makes a dive, y'see.

rows.label: tlk43310148_02_msg0004
rows.name:
Whoever smashed it open must have
had some pretty awesome power at
their command, I tell you.
